title: Justice Ejaz Swati takes oath as acting CJ of BHC - Pakistan - DAWN.COM
content:
QUETTA: Justice Muhammad Ejaz Swati on Friday took the oath of the acting chief justice of Balochistan High Court.

Balochistan Governor Sheikh Jaffar Khan Mandokhail administered the oath to Justice Swati at a ceremony held at the Governor House.

The ceremony was attended by judges of the Balochistan High Court, senior lawyers and government officials.

Published in Dawn, February 15th, 2025
